        </div>
        <h3 class="font-sans text-xl font-semibold text-[#292524]">Social Media</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 font-sans text-sm text-[#79716b]">AI posts across Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, and X.</p>
        <div class="mt-5">
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1">
            <span class="currency-symbol font-sans text-[42px] font-bold tracking-tight text-[#292524]">$</span><span class="font-sans text-[42px] font-bold tracking-tight text-[#292524]" id="mod-social-price">41</span>
