        <a href="/demo/" class="mt-6 flex h-[44px] w-full items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-[#615fff] bg-[#615fff] font-sans text-[15px] font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-[#4f39f6]">Book a Demo</a>
